		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/以索忒.assets/Image_21.png')" x="1268" y="171" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/以索忒.assets/Image_22.png')" x="1248" y="150" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/以索忒.assets/Image_23.png')" x="596" y="395" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/以索忒.assets/Image_24.png')" x="576" y="374" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/以索忒.assets/Image_25.png')" x="596" y="683" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/以索忒.assets/Image_26.png')" x="576" y="662" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="424" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">霜役人的元素爆发命中所累加的生命之契大小等同于自身<span color="#ff9999">16%</span><span>的攻击力，且在该生命之契的影响下，目标敌人将每秒流失</span><span color="#dfbfff">(0.4%HP+72)</span><span>的生命值(后台停5%)，其与生命之契同生共死，持续10min。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/以索忒.assets/Image_27.png')" x="1393" y="362">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/以索忒.assets/Image_28.png')" x="1268" y="395" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/以索忒.assets/Image_29.png')" x="1248" y="374" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="990" width="1094" height="62" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="32" fontWeight="bold" color="#bfffff">固有天赋·锃锋<span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">：元素爆发的追加攻击对附有生命之契的目标造成的伤害提升</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ff9999">150%</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">。被施加生命之契的目标，在遭受每段追加「猎杀」时都会累积生命之契。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="894" width="1112" height="62" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="32" fontWeight="bold" color="#bfffff">固有天赋·留刃<span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">：爆发的第一段伤害命中时，</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffedbf">恢复5%生命值</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">；生命值</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffedbf">低于20%</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">时，施放元素爆发改为</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffedbf">消耗10%当前生命值</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1104" width="312" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">拥有90%的冻结抵抗。<br/><span color="#99ffff">以索忒总是施放连招，常见的连招有：<br/></span><span>EEE、EEA、EZA、AZ、ZE、AEE、AEZ。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
	</Group>
</Graphic>